  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the final frontier — where survival isn’t a right, it’s a fight.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stars End</i> is a player-hosted/solo sci-fi survival sandbox set hundreds of years in the future, in a star system colonized by humans escaping a dying Earth. What was meant to be a second chance has become a lawless frontier — a place where every scrap, bullet, and building must be earned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out here, you’ll wrangle resources from dangerous planets, fend off alien wildlife (watch out for bears), and build your own base — be it a frontier shack or a fortified space station. Explore procedurally generated worlds on foot, horseback, or by starship, then blast into orbit and continue the fight in space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or host your own server as you stake a claim in a persistent galaxy where survival is tough, but freedom is yours to take. Whether you're settling the land or raiding for loot, <i>Stars End</i> gives you the tools — and the grit — to shape your own path.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Planets</strong> – Each world is unique, with varied biomes, threats, and resources to uncover.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Survival Experience</strong> – Battle alien wildlife, endure hostile environments, and scavenge for the materials needed to stay alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Base, Your Way</strong> – Construct rugged cabins, fortified outposts, or advanced space stations with a deep crafting and construction system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PvE and PvP Combat</strong> – Engage in tense FPS-style battles against AI factions or rival survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore Land and Space</strong> – Traverse the terrain by vehicle or horse,  then seamlessly launch into orbit aboard your personal starship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo or Player-Hosted Servers</strong> – Play alone, with friends, or open your world to others via custom servers.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Persistent Open World</strong> – Build, explore, and take on story-driven missions across procedurally generated planets in a  sci-fi sandbox.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the final frontier — where survival isn’t a right, it’s a fight.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/1c252c737f35120562ef6a303802aa0e.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stars End</i> is a player-hosted/solo sci-fi survival sandbox set hundreds of years in the future, in a star system colonized by humans escaping a dying Earth. What was meant to be a second chance has become a lawless frontier — a place where every scrap, bullet, and building must be earned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out here, you’ll wrangle resources from dangerous planets, fend off alien wildlife (watch out for bears), and build your own base — be it a frontier shack or a fortified space station. Explore procedurally generated worlds on foot, horseback, or by starship, then blast into orbit and continue the fight in space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/441c4ec960fd9556a613a4bfe75a51bb.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or host your own server as you stake a claim in a persistent galaxy where survival is tough, but freedom is yours to take. Whether you're settling the land or raiding for loot, <i>Stars End</i> gives you the tools — and the grit — to shape your own path.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Planets</strong> – Each world is unique, with varied biomes, threats, and resources to uncover.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Survival Experience</strong> – Battle alien wildlife, endure hostile environments, and scavenge for the materials needed to stay alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/89712b8bb013aa8bb19b3962048f0900.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Base, Your Way</strong> – Construct rugged cabins, fortified outposts, or advanced space stations with a deep crafting and construction system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PvE and PvP Combat</strong> – Engage in tense FPS-style battles against AI factions or rival survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore Land and Space</strong> – Traverse the terrain by vehicle or horse,  then seamlessly launch into orbit aboard your personal starship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.poster.avif?t=1768953144\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.webm?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/623340/extras/7daab4d1fc6d409bef8eba65564f2146.mp4?t=1768953144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo or Player-Hosted Servers</strong> – Play alone, with friends, or open your world to others via custom servers.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Persistent Open World</strong> – Build, explore, and take on story-driven missions across procedurally generated planets in a  sci-fi sandbox.</p></li></ul>",
